<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Data Deletion Instructions">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <title>Data Deletion Request</title>

    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
        }

        body{
            font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background:#f5f7fa;
            color:#333;
            line-height:1.8;
        }

        header{
            background:#0d6efd;
            color:#fff;
            padding:30px 20px;
            text-align:center;
        }

        .container{
            max-width:1000px;
            margin:40px auto;
            background:#fff;
            padding:40px;
            border-radius:10px;
            box-shadow:0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        }

        h1{
            margin-bottom:10px;
        }

        h2{
            margin-top:35px;
            margin-bottom:10px;
            color:#0d6efd;
        }

        p{
            margin-bottom:15px;
        }

        ul{
            margin-left:20px;
            margin-bottom:15px;
        }

        li{
            margin-bottom:8px;
        }

        a{
            color:#0d6efd;
            text-decoration:none;
        }

        a:hover{
            text-decoration:underline;
        }

        .last-updated{
            color:#666;
            font-size:15px;
            margin-top:10px;
        }

        .email-box{
            background:#f1f5ff;
            border-left:5px solid #0d6efd;
            padding:15px;
            margin-top:20px;
            border-radius:5px;
        }

        footer{
            text-align:center;
            padding:25px;
            background:#222;
            color:#fff;
            margin-top:40px;
        }

        @media(max-width:768px){
            .container{
                margin:20px;
                padding:25px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Data Deletion Request</h1>
    <p>Request the deletion of your personal data.</p>
    <p class="last-updated">
        Last Updated: January 1, 2026
    </p>
</header>

<div class="container">

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>

    <p>
        We respect your privacy and provide you with the ability to request
        the deletion of your personal information that we have collected.
        This page explains how you can submit a data deletion request.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Your Right to Delete Data</h2>

    <p>
        You have the right to request the deletion of your personal
        information stored by our website or application, subject to
        applicable legal obligations.
    </p>

    <h2>3. How to Request Data Deletion</h2>

    <p>
        To request deletion of your data, please send us an email containing
        the following information:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>Your Full Name</li>
        <li>Your Registered Email Address</li>
        <li>Your User ID (if applicable)</li>
        <li>Reason for the deletion request (optional)</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="email-box">
        <strong>Email:</strong> your@email.com
    </div>

    <h2>4. Processing Time</h2>

    <p>
        After receiving your request, we will verify your identity and
        process your request within 30 days, unless a longer period is
        required by applicable law.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Information That May Be Retained</h2>

    <p>
        Certain information may be retained where required for legal,
        regulatory, fraud prevention, security, accounting, or other
        legitimate business purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>

    <p>
        If your information has been shared with trusted third-party
        service providers, we will make reasonable efforts to notify
        those providers of your deletion request where applicable.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Account Deletion</h2>

    <p>
        If you have an account with us, requesting deletion may permanently
        remove your profile, account information, saved preferences,
        and any associated content. This action may be irreversible.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>

    <p>
        If you have questions regarding your data or this deletion process,
        please contact us using the information below.
    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> your@email.com<br>
        <strong>Website:</strong> https://yourwebsite.com
    </p>

</div>

<footer>
    &copy; 2026 Your Website. All Rights Reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
